Author: 297al
Text: I can kinda relate. My mum is always talking about how whenever my sister gains a few kilos she just skips a meal here and there and is back to a regular weight. Makes me feel like shit about myself especially when I try to eat normally

Author: byie
Text: Exactlyyy.  I can’t stand when someone does “starving themselves better” than me. It’s like a competition for me or something-
